Package org.youscope.common.job.basicjobs

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChangePositionJob
    A job to change the stage's position.
    CompositeJob
    A job which consists of other jobs.
    ContinuousImagingJob  
    DeviceSettingJob  
    FocusingJob  
    ImagingJob
    A job which makes a microscope image in the defined channel.
    ScriptingJob
    A scripting job executes a script every time it runs, and-depending on the script-its child jobs.
    StatisticsJob
    Interface of a measurement job which collects statistical data about the evaluation and appends it to a file.
    WaitJob
    A job for waiting a given time.
